        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "**A biological / balneological-style folio.** Despite the filename, this isn't one of the famous radial cosmological diagrams — it's a multi-zone page with a central vertical figure of nude women descending through a blue-canopied form, surrounded by paragraph-blocks of Voynichese, with a separate green herbal-like bulb at the bottom right. Pages like this dominate the manuscript's middle quires.",
